Synopsis Edit

In the world, the manipulation of tanks (Sensha-do) is one of the traditional martial arts especially for girls. Miho doesn't like Sensha-do and moves to Ooarai Girl's High School. But the chairperson of the student council orders Miho to participate in the Senshadou Mandatory Class on threat of expulsion from school, But changes her mind
